  "segments": [
    {
      "idx": 0,
      "start_ms": 660,
      "end_ms": 5300,
      "text": "야유는 서둘러 방으로 들어간다 고등학교 시절 사진을 꺼내 하나씩 확인했다",
      "target_text": "Yayu hurriedly entered the room and took out photos from high school to check one by one.",
      "audio_path": "speech/0001_660_5300.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/0e48103988bf4715a1cf3eff4a181078/speech/0001_660_5300.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 1,
      "start_ms": 5580,
      "end_ms": 10360,
      "text": "상대가 옛동창 시우라는 사실을 알아챘다 반가운 마음에 잠시 들렀다 가라고",
      "target_text": "He realized that the other person was his old classmate, Siwoo, and felt happy to see him.",
      "audio_path": "speech/0002_5580_10360.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/0e48103988bf4715a1cf3eff4a181078/speech/0002_5580_10360.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 2,
      "start_ms": 10360,
      "end_ms": 11280,
      "text": "권하려 했다",
      "target_text": "He tried to suggest that Siwoo stay for a while.",
      "audio_path": "speech/0003_10360_11280.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/0e48103988bf4715a1cf3eff4a181078/speech/0003_10360_11280.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 3,
      "start_ms": 11720,
      "end_ms": 15400,
      "text": "하지만 시우는 말했다 다른 주문도 배달하러 가야 한다고 했다",
      "target_text": "But Siwoo said he had to go deliver another order.",
      "audio_path": "speech/0004_11720_15400.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/0e48103988bf4715a1cf3eff4a181078/speech/0004_11720_15400.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 4,
      "start_ms": 15700,
      "end_ms": 19740,
      "text": "괜히 시간을 뺏고 싶지 않았기에 두 사람은 가볍게 인사만 나눴다.",
      "target_text": "Not wanting to waste time unnecessarily, the two just exchanged light greetings.",
      "audio_path": "speech/0005_15700_19740.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/0e48103988bf4715a1cf3eff4a181078/speech/0005_15700_19740.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 5,
      "start_ms": 19860,
      "end_ms": 24400,
      "text": "그리고 시우는 급히 자리를 떠났다 방으로 돌아온 야유는 생각할수록",
      "target_text": "After Siwoo quickly left, Yayu returned to his room and the more he thought about it,",
      "audio_path": "speech/0006_19860_24400.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/0e48103988bf4715a1cf3eff4a181078/speech/0006_19860_24400.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 6,
      "start_ms": 24400,
      "end_ms": 26320,
      "text": "아쉬움이 더욱 커져만 갔다",
      "target_text": "the greater his sense of regret grew.",
      "audio_path": "speech/0007_24400_26320.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/0e48103988bf4715a1cf3eff4a181078/speech/0007_24400_26320.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 7,
      "start_ms": 26320,
      "end_ms": 31540,
      "text": "어느덧 서른을 앞둔 나이가 되었지만 외모는 학창시절과 크게 달라지지 않았다.",
      "target_text": "Now approaching thirty, his appearance had not changed much from his school days.",
      "audio_path": "speech/0008_26320_31540.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/0e48103988bf4715a1cf3eff4a181078/speech/0008_26320_31540.wav"
    }
  ]
